spans.content: EDWARDS Fire Alarm Bells are specially designed for fire alarm
applications. The gongs are made of selected alloy steel to give
the loud, resonant tones necessary in fire alarm systems.
Two gong sizes are available to overcome different ambient noise
The Fire Alarm Bells are of the underdome type with heavy duty
mechanisms. Each bell is supplied with a mounting plate that fits
any standard single-gang opening (see Installation Data). For
weather-proof application EDWARDS offers an optional surface
weatherproof back box. Refer to the Specification chart for ap-
plicability and cata-log number of the weatherproof back box for
Finish — Standard gong and housing furnished gray with red
label. Optional red finish available. Add Suffix “R” to Catalog
FM — 438 and 439 Series Bells shown below are FM approved.
